@startuml
left to right direction
actor Trader
rectangle "Traders Mirror" {
  usecase "Record Trade" as U1
  usecase "Edit Trade" as U4
  usecase "Analyze Performance" as U2
  usecase "Track Metrics" as U3
  usecase "Export/Import" as U5
}
Trader --> U1
Trader --> U4
Trader --> U2
Trader --> U3
Trader --> U5

note right of U2
  Analyses:
  - Winrate
  - Average PnL
  - Risk/Reward
  - Equity Curve
end note

note left of U5
  Export: CSV/JSON
  Import: JSON (normalized DTO)
end note
@enduml
